                                                                    Project 1
Scenario : Create Amazon Dynamo DB Table using default table setting. The table name must be “Student” and the Partition key must be “rollno” – Number Type. Add these items in the table “Student.”

Rollno(Number) Name(String)
20     Amit
30     Anil
40      Aman  
Query the rollnumber 20 and Delete the Amazon Dynamo DB Table “Student.”

Actions that need to be done
>Create table “Student” with Partition Key “rollno” and default table settings
>Add item rollno 20 and Name Amit
>Add item rollno 30 and Name Anil
>Add item rollno 40 and Name Aman
>Query rollno 20 data
>Delete the Amazon Dynamo DB Table “Student”


